archimate:Constraint.name: Ensure compliance does not result in a duplication of collecting domain name registration data by for example collaborating with domain name registration services
archimate:Constraint.documentation: 6. Compliance with the obligations laid down in paragraphs 1 to 5 shall not result in a duplication of collecting domain name registration data. To that end, Member States shall require TLD name registries and entities providing domain name registration services to cooperate with each other.
